OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Sense of shame' over      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FMethodist Church abuse     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcases                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, There is sorrow and a "sense of shame" 
OL,6, within the Methodist Church in Ireland 
OL,7, after a review identified 30 historic  
OL,8, abuses cases, its president has said.  
OL,10,FThe Reverend David Turtle was speaking 
OL,11,Ftwo days after the Church published the
OL,12,Ffindings of its three-year review into 
OL,13,Fhow it dealt with abuse allegations.   
OL,15,FThe report examined Methodist records  
OL,16,Ffrom 1950 onwards and found six abuse  
OL,17,Fcases involved ordained ministers.     
OL,19,FMost of the 30 cases were allegations  
OL,20,Fagainst lay volunteer leaders.         
